msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which a sum is performed.  The default, axis=None, will "
"sum all of the elements of the input array.  If axis is negative it counts "
"from the last to the first axis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.sum:17
msgid ""
"If axis is a tuple of ints, a sum is performed on all of the axes specified "
"in the tuple instead of a single axis or all the axes as before."
msgstr ""

